msg: $date is passed undef to progress, so I added in a "set to 0 if undefined"
to at least stop the warning.  $total_count is set to 0 in the parent,
then each child increases their copy, then the parent calls progress which
still sees $total_count==0.  So I moved the increment into the parent.
